From: Vincenzo Grimaldi <vince.ceccarelli@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 14:51:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] fix(deploy): build and deploy on Vercel with zero env
 vars

- Clerk is now optional: middleware is a pass-through and ClerkProvider/
  header auth UI mount only when keys are present (lib/auth.ts flag)
- Supabase client is guarded and lazy; importing it can no longer throw
- Geist fonts self-hosted via the geist package: no Google Fonts network
  fetch at build time (removes a build-environment failure mode)
- Honest metadata; removed reference to non-existent /og-image.jpg
- Added .env.example (un-ignored) documenting every variable is optional
