From 8dd4a0ef69c4aff3ad5a9594f4f39dfeacdd8905 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vincenzo Grimaldi <vince.ceccarelli@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 14:51:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] fix(honesty): remove all fabricated metrics,
 testimonials, and deployment claims

Removed: '850+ robots deployed', '98.7% first-pass approval', '3.2x faster',
'+41% margin', three invented customer testimonials with fake company names,
'booked 3-5 months out', fake 'InteriorFinish Technologies, Inc.' entity,
'free trial' CTAs for a product that does not exist, dead resources links,
decorative social icons pointing at platform homepages, and links to
dryforge.ai/paintforge.ai domains.

Replaced with truthful early-stage positioning:
- Pilot-program recruitment as the single conversion path (WaitlistCTA:
  Formspree if configured, mailto fallback -- never a dead button)
- ROI calculator reframed as a transparent model with stated assumptions
- Pricing labeled as planned/indicative
- Chatbot labeled as a scripted demo, fabricated stats stripped
- Dashboard carries an unmissable SAMPLE DATA banner
- Fixed pre-existing react-hooks/purity lint error and unused imports
